title: Natalie's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Mediterranean, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This restaurant is set up like a sub shop, order to-go or sit in. Offers 4 kinds of veggie burgers (lentil-millet, eggplant-tofu, zucchini-pine nut, broccoli-cashew). Lebanese/Greek dishes such as falafel, vegetarian kibby, grape leaves, and ratatouille. Several salads/dishes can be made vegan by ordering without feta. Also offers basic American fare such as french fries, grilled sandwiches, subs.
